            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/yimulanhanlutoushe.jpg?VersionId=AKQahFSG4QThQY.FtftyYczrmt6WfGFx&itok=c4NFE7je" title="巴基斯坦总理伊姆兰汗确定将出席下月的北京冬奥会开幕式。（路透社档案照片）" alt="巴基斯坦总理伊姆兰汗确定将出席下月的北京冬奥会开幕式。（路透社档案照片）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/yimulanhanlutoushe.jpg?VersionId=AKQahFSG4QThQY.FtftyYczrmt6WfGFx&itok=c4NFE7je" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
